msg":"借位讚一讚，係停車場拍到班狗屌9手足嗰條ss片。<br />\n<br />\n記者如果琴晚比班狗見到真係死硬，感謝你嘅勇氣。令其他人睇到呢條極醜惡嘅片段。留名睇PPRB點解話"},{"pid":"7eb08c7c84633c0127f283a7554a0aa8d4d1e559","tid":1917633,"uid":151770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"Agger 推"},{"pid":"599c278b2fae17a9d5fa41a05772f1fbe1f17a0a","tid":1917633,"uid":54220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8988f45d555f73917320982b9a29544260160f45","tid":1917633,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}